high_descs: turn around towards the center table
pick up the knife on the table
turn around and head for the table
slice the tomato on the table
turn left and head for the fridge
place the knife inside the fridge
turn right towards the table
pick up a slice from the table
move left towards the fridge
place the tomato to cool and then take it out
turn around and head for the bin
trash the tomato in it
Turn to face the island counter.
Pick the knife up off of the counter.
Turn around and face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Move to the right and turn to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the knife inside.
Go to the right and face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Move to the left and turn to face the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge and close the door and then open the door and take the tomato out.
Cross the room and turn to face the trash can in the corner.
Put the tomato in the trash can in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a tomato in a trash can.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Pick up a knife on the kitchen island, to the right of the loaf of bread.
Go to the counter behind you, adjacent to the fridge.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Go to the fridge to your left.
Put the knife in the fridge, on the bottom shelf.
Return to the counter, adjacent to the fridge.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Go to the fridge to your left.
Chill the tomato slice in the fridge.
Turn left, move forward, turn left, move forward, then turn right to face the trash bin.
Put the tomato slice in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of tomato in the trash.
